		(property "Description" "12-bit resolution  +/- 1 LSB max DNL  +/- 1 LSB max INL (MCP3204/3208-B)  +/- 2 LSB max INL (MCP3204/3208-C)  4 (MCP3204) or 8 (MCP3208) input channels  Analog inputs programmable as single-ended or pseudo-differential pairs  On-chip sample and hold  SPI serial interface (modes 0,0 and 1,1)  Single supply operation: 2.7V - 5.5V  100 ksps max. sampling rate at VDD = 5V  50 ksps max. sampling rate at VDD = 2.7V  Low power CMOS technology: - 500 nA typical standby current, 2 A max. - 400 A"
